---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
title: "Contact - Contractor Software Hub"
description: "Have a question about a review, want to suggest software we should cover, or need to reach our editorial team?"
---

<header class="bg-[#0f172a] text-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Contact Us</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">Have a question about a review, want to suggest software we should cover, or need to reach our editorial team?</p>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
  <section class="mb-12">
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">Have a question about a review? Spotted an error? Know of a software tool we haven't covered? We want to hear from you.</p>

    <div class="bg-[#f8fafc] border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Send a message</h3>
      <p class="mb-4"><a href="mailto:chris@contractorsoftwarehub.com" class="text-[#0f172a] underline hover:text-[#22c55e] font-medium">chris@contractorsoftwarehub.com</a></p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">We read everything and try to respond within a few business days.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">What we're happy to hear about</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-3 ml-5 mb-6 text-gray-700">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-[#22c55e] font-bold mt-0.5">•</span>
        <span>Questions about reviews or recommendations</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-[#22c55e] font-bold mt-0.5">•</span>
        <span>Software tools we should cover</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-[#22c55e] font-bold mt-0.5">•</span>
        <span>Corrections or feedback on existing content</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-[#22c55e] font-bold mt-0.5">•</span>
        <span>Your experience with a tool we've reviewed</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Note:</strong> We don't accept guest posts or paid placements at this time.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Business Address</h2>
    <address class="not-italic text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Contractor Software Hub LLC<br />
      c/o Northwest Registered Agent<br />
      116 Agnes Rd Ste 200<br />
      Knoxville, TN 37919
    </address>
  </section>
</main>

<footer class="bg-[#0f172a] text-gray-400 text-sm">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">Reviews</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/blog/jobber-review/" class="hover:text-white">Jobber Review</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/housecall-pro-review/" class="hover:text-white">Housecall Pro Review</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/servicetitan-review/" class="hover:text-white">ServiceTitan Review</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">Compare</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/blog/jobber-vs-housecall-pro/" class="hover:text-white">Jobber vs Housecall Pro</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/servicetitan-vs-jobber/" class="hover:text-white">ServiceTitan vs Jobber</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/housecall-pro-vs-fieldedge/" class="hover:text-white">Housecall Pro vs FieldEdge</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">About</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/about/" class="hover:text-white">About CSH</a></li>
          <li><a href="/affiliate-disclosure/" class="hover:text-white">Affiliate Disclosure</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact/" class="hover:text-white">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-t border-gray-700 pt-8">
      <p class="mb-2">Independent reviews for contractors who'd rather be building.</p>
      <p>&copy; 2026 ContractorSoftwareHub.com. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
